For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Lickitung (TCG Pocket).

Lickitung has been featured on 21 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Lickitung cards are normally Colorless-type Basic Pokémon.
